{"id":"zacher","term":"Zacher","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Memorial, a son of Jehiel (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 8:31\">1 Chr. 8:31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 9:35\">9:35</a>); called Zechariah (9:37).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 8:31","1 Chronicles 9:35"]}